data.description: Priced to sell!!!!Welcome Home !  This move in ready gem has 5 bedrooms and 3 full bathrooms. Formal dining room, pass through pantry between kitchen and formal dining room. Spacious great room perfect for relaxing or fun get togethers. Kitchen with large island, bright windows and expansive granite counter space.  You will love the pass through pantry area to the dining area. Bedroom downstairs with 3/4 bathroom is perfect for guests! Primary suite has small retreat area and an ensuite bath with upgraded counter tops and shower upgraded counters. Large loft upstairs can provide an extra space for relaxing . Laundry room has room for additional shelving if you like to add for more storage. Additional bedrooms are large .  The backyard is completed and the swing set will remain! . Landscape is water smart.  The location has a community pool and plenty of opportunity to enjoy the great outdoors.  This is move in ready and an excellant home with loads of space!
